Title: One Day in the Life of Anton Baklanov
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (created by), Stephen Schiff, Tracey Scott Wilson
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Lev Gorn, Annet Mahendru
Plot: Philip and Elizabeth's home and work lives collide in new and dangerous ways. Nina struggles to figure out her next steps. Arkady assigns Oleg and Tatiana to an operation with uncertain potential.
